387
00:18:12,840 --> 00:18:15,000
But elevating a personal opinion

388
00:18:15,520 --> 00:18:17,120
to artifact authentication

389
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:20,760
is definitely beyond the scope of a student.

390
00:18:21,080 --> 00:18:21,760
Principal,

391
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:22,560
Xu Xiao

392
00:18:22,560 --> 00:18:24,360
