396
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:31,520
Now they regret it and come to the school to make a scene.

397
00:18:31,520 --> 00:18:32,600
Isn't this nonsense?

398
00:18:32,600 --> 00:18:33,530
Yes, Principal.

399
00:18:33,720 --> 00:18:34,240
But...

400
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:37,360
If they keep making trouble for the school,

401
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:38,970
