403
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:42,660
Principal,

404
00:18:43,520 --> 00:18:45,600
if we discipline Xu Xiao for this,

405
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:47,840
wouldn't that indirectly

406
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:49,080
mean admitting

407
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:50,180
that the school

408
00:18:50,480 --> 00:18:52,080
