417
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:07,160
Okay.

418
00:19:11,040 --> 00:19:11,640
Intel.

419
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:14,240
The school decided not to punish Xu Xiao for now.

420
00:19:14,240 --> 00:19:14,720
But

421
00:19:14,840 --> 00:19:16,120
