422
00:19:16,120 --> 00:19:17,440
Then it should be fine.

423
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:19,200
With the school involved,

424
00:19:19,200 --> 00:19:21,260
Zhang Jiatian can't act recklessly.

425
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:23,280
I have something to do. I...

426
00:19:24,480 --> 00:19:27,140
Are you distressed about the broken porcelain?

427
00:19:27,320 --> 00:19:29,120
Couldn't he be more perceptive?

428
00:19:29,320 --> 00:19:31,680
Every piece of porcelain had a name on the bottom.

429
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:33,320
He should have aimed better if he wanted to smash them.

430
00:19:33,320 --> 00:19:34,160
What do you know?

431
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:36,160
That was an indiscriminate attack.

432
00:19:36,520 --> 00:19:37,760
Judging by his stance,

433
00:19:37,760 --> 00:19:40,200
I believe he's the kind to smash his own bowl.

434
00:19:40,200 --> 00:19:42,260
Smashing anyone's is unacceptable.

435
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:45,400
I had planned to keep my work

436
00:19:45,520 --> 00:19:47,580
as a souvenir after this exhibition.

437
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,640
Everyone has worked hard for days.

438
00:19:54,640 --> 00:19:56,970
Why don't we go out for a meal to celebrate?

439
00:19:57,120 --> 00:19:57,920
It's my treat.

440
00:19:58,520 --> 00:19:59,760
Then hurry up.

441
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:00,840
Everyone who hears gets a share.

442
00:20:00,840 --> 00:20:01,280
I want to go too.

443
00:20:01,280 --> 00:20:01,680
Me too.

444
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:02,640
As soon as you heard the class monitor is treating,

445
00:20:02,640 --> 00:20:04,040
you all want to go, right?

446
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:05,640
I didn't say I wouldn't bring you two.

447
00:20:05,640 --> 00:20:07,240
Let's go and see what to eat.

448
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:09,120
Xu Xiao.

449
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:12,080
I'm sorry.

450
00:20:13,120 --> 00:20:13,920
Because of me,

451
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:16,920
the porcelain you worked so hard to make was smashed.

452
00:20:16,920 --> 00:20:18,200
It was clearly their fault.

453
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:19,080
You don't need to apologize.

454
00:20:19,080 --> 00:20:20,000
Let's go eat together.

455
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:21,680
Yeah, let's have something good.

456
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:22,080
Let's go together

457
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:24,040
