458
00:20:24,040 --> 00:20:24,700
No, thanks.

459
00:20:25,040 --> 00:20:26,100
I'll go back first.

460
00:20:37,280 --> 00:20:38,940
What did I tell you at the time?

461
00:20:39,320 --> 00:20:41,800
We shouldn't have let him apply to this school.

462
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:43,400
You insisted that the child had grown up,

463
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:45,460
and we should respect his interests.

464
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:46,580
And the result?

465
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,240
He is still a student,

466
00:20:48,280 --> 00:20:49,840
yet he has caused such a huge incident.

467
00:20:49,840 --> 00:20:51,680
What will happen when he grows up?

468
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:54,280
The school didn't say it was our child's fault.

469
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:56,040
How could it not be him?

470
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:59,000
You know how obsessed he is

471
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:00,200
