472
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:00,640
No.

473
00:21:01,080 --> 00:21:02,440
He likes to study things.

474
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:03,360
That's a good thing.

475
00:21:03,360 --> 00:21:04,960
If he studies in this field,

476
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:08,240
