477
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:10,570
Who can guarantee he won't offend anyone?

478
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:13,760
Over the years, there have been plenty of people around us

479
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:15,400
whose families were ruined.

480
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:17,720
I am a living example.

481
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:19,640
Every year in this market,

482
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:21,840
