483
00:21:22,640 --> 00:21:24,400
The old one is already crazy,

484
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:25,880
and now the young one.

485
00:21:28,200 --> 00:21:29,130
This profession

486
00:21:29,280 --> 00:21:30,680
really does a lot of harm.

487
00:21:31,440 --> 00:21:33,240
I really don't know why he,

488
00:21:33,480 --> 00:21:34,880
