492
00:21:38,040 --> 00:21:39,320
Alright, drink some water.

493
00:21:39,320 --> 00:21:40,520
He was still young then.

494
00:21:40,520 --> 00:21:41,120
Yes, yes.

495
00:21:41,120 --> 00:21:42,560
He definitely doesn't know

496
00:21:42,560 --> 00:21:45,320
