497
00:22:03,560 --> 00:22:04,420
Let me tell you.

498
00:22:04,600 --> 00:22:06,000
I will never divorce you.

499
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:08,400
And you are definitely not getting our son.

500
00:22:21,760 --> 00:22:22,960
Everyone.

501
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:24,240
Look at this.

502
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:25,600
Look.

503
00:22:26,280 --> 00:22:27,120
What is this?

504
00:22:27,360 --> 00:22:28,160
What's going on?

505
00:22:28,160 --> 00:22:29,120
This is the guy causing trouble for Xu Xiao.

506
00:22:29,120 --> 00:22:30,250
Let's go take a look.

507
00:22:30,560 --> 00:22:31,220
That's him.

508
00:22:31,600 --> 00:22:32,460
It's him again.

509
00:22:32,880 --> 00:22:34,760
I hope he's not looking for trouble with our class.

510
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:36,120
It looks like he's livestreaming.

511
00:22:36,120 --> 00:22:37,160
Xu Jinsong.

512
00:22:37,400 --> 00:22:39,280
This guy relied on his past

513
00:22:39,280 --> 00:22:41,080
ability to restore cultural relics,

514
00:22:41,080 --> 00:22:45,040
bought an imitation Ming Chenghua porcelain at a low price,

515
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,800
repackaged it,

516
00:22:46,960 --> 00:22:50,090
and sold it to a buyer at a high price as a genuine antique.

517
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:51,120
Then this buyer

518
00:22:51,160 --> 00:22:53,120
