519
00:22:53,120 --> 00:22:54,880
It turned out to be a fake.

520
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:55,640
What kind of person is he?

521
00:22:55,640 --> 00:22:57,640
What kind of good son could he raise?

522
00:22:57,680 --> 00:22:59,520
And he says our stuff is fake.

523
00:22:59,600 --> 00:23:00,840
Who are you?

524
00:23:01,560 --> 00:23:02,160
Come here.

525
00:23:02,280 --> 00:23:03,040
It's him.

526
00:23:03,320 --> 00:23:04,520
He is Xu Jinsong's son.

527
00:23:04,520 --> 00:23:04,840
Don't move.

528
00:23:04,840 --> 00:23:05,360
Xu Xiao.

529
00:23:05,360 --> 00:23:06,240
I have already explained this.

530
00:23:06,240 --> 00:23:07,040
Stop being unreasonable.

531
00:23:07,040 --> 00:23:08,120
I'm being unreasonable?

532
00:23:08,120 --> 00:23:09,240
Look, that's him.

533
00:23:09,240 --> 00:23:09,960
He is Xu Xiao.

534
00:23:09,960 --> 00:23:10,360
Move away.

535
00:23:10,360 --> 00:23:11,360
Watch your mouth.

536
00:23:11,400 --> 00:23:11,840
Stop fighting.

537
00:23:11,840 --> 00:23:12,640
Or I'll call the police.

538
00:23:12,640 --> 00:23:13,400
I'm calling the police.

539
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:14,600
This is our school gate.

540
00:23:14,600 --> 00:23:15,200
Move away.

541
00:23:22,560 --> 00:23:23,890
Do you have time to talk?

542
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:28,600
Xu Xiao?

543
00:23:29,920 --> 00:23:32,920
It's no use letting this situation escalate further.

544
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:34,850
I've already contacted Mr. Zhang.

545
00:23:34,880 --> 00:23:35,960
He hopes

546
00:23:36,800 --> 00:23:38,800
