547
00:23:40,240 --> 00:23:42,120
I didn't do anything wrong. Why should I apologize?

548
00:23:42,120 --> 00:23:43,640
Don't rush to explain.

549
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:45,920
It's no longer about right or wrong.

550
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:48,000
That person's

551
00:23:48,280 --> 00:23:49,560
scandal was dug up,

552
00:23:49,800 --> 00:23:51,060
