570
00:24:24,160 --> 00:24:24,920
Okay.

571
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:29,210
I won't suspend my studies.

572
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,600
And I won't apologize either.

573
00:24:31,600 --> 00:24:32,600
